    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you choose this school at 2nd level, you learn the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.oIzA2MEHwxhtQneU]{Minor Illusion} cantrip. If you already know this cantrip, you learn a different wizard cantrip of your choice. The cantrip doesn't count against your number of cantrips known.</p>\n<p>When you cast @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.oIzA2MEHwxhtQneU]{Minor Illusion}, you can create both a sound and an image with a single casting of the spell, and when you create an image, its maximum size is a 10-foot cube instead of a 5-foot cube.</p>",
